data.description: 57+or- acres. Great hunting and grazing. Loaded with oak trees, a wet weather creek and 3 tanks. 9 strand barbed wire fence on back and most of one side, rest of fence is net and will hold cows. 2009 built brick house with covered front porch, 3 nice size bedrooms, 2 with walk in closets, 2 bathrooms, large utility room, kitchen with granite counter tops and a double carport on the back. Backyard Smoke House with Outside Firebox. All of this on a paved road. Old farmhouse and 1+acres next door can be bought with this​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ property.
